{"tid":2292696,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立製錶師 :)","createTime":"2020-11-19T16:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T16:27:46.000Z","uid":205041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d20fc11f30a97eb139965d068bdf3b2417ec25ca","tid":2292696,"uid":205041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"浅冈肇😀👍🏾 有冇同好？<br />\n<br />\n「Hajime Asaoka（淺岡肇）是來自日本東京的獨立制表師。畢業自東京大學的「藝術與職業前景推動」及「圖形工程設計」，後來通過自學，成為一名制表人。據聞，他曾在公寓里獨自完成螺絲、齒輪等等的製作。2011年發佈的一件作品就是陀飛輪腕表「Tourbillon #1」，獲得日本表壇高度關注。2015年，就加入了得有一些江湖地位才會獲准加入的AHCI獨立制表人學會。而Kurono這個牌子的目標，就是以更親民的價格，推出更多Hajime Asaoka所設計的腕表。<br />\n<br />\n今年，Kurono分別入圍了GPHG的最佳挑戰獎和最佳計時碼表兩項大獎。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n25th Nov 出新錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkMrDox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkMrDox.png&h=7b934aee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNKXK3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNKXK3z.png&h=0065b006&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8DEYoB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8DEYoB.png&h=bf83a19f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ywSyWX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ywSyWX.png&h=74d8f373&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3689Bai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3689Bai.png&h=07f923d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他 獨立製錶師 介紹下"}]}